user.biography:
Premium baby necessities made for modern mamas
Organic cotton + buttery soft knit fabrics
swaddles, bibs, 3-layer quilts, gowns, headbands
& more 🤍

node.text:
It’s AUSSIE time mate! This new collection is one we’ve been so excited to share with you!! We’re so grateful to have Copper Pearl in Australia and we wanted to show our support to all our Aussie friends with this new print! 

Check out the video above and let us know if you have any questions 👇🏼 we hope you ❤️ it as much as we do!

node.text:
HALLOWEEN!!! Eeek! Our TRICK + TREAT + PATCH collections are now available! 🎃🌽🦇 we have so many goodies in these new + returning lines that we’re sure you’ll find something you love. These are up on our website now + a handful will be on amazon soon (we can update you when). You can also shop local using our store locator on our website! Our Halloween collection is limited edition so grab them while you can 🖤
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Tag a Halloween loving friend and let us know if you have questions 👇🏼

node.text:
🎥 @morganreneemcintyre

"Our story for those of you who don’t know. My pain had a purpose and so does yours, my friend. Miscarriage, infant loss, or infertility are such hard things to go through so I want to use my story to encourage as many other women as I can! 💕"

Late night GIVEAWAY! How stinking cute are all of these colors? This is all of our solids in one picture. Swipe to see all the names! We wanna giveaway 3️⃣ $50 gift cards to buy some new solids.
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
To enter all you gotta do is: 
• like or save this post
• tell us your FAVE solid color from above 
• tag as many real friends as you’d like 
• for some extra points share this post to your stories and tag us (not required, but always appreciated 🤍) 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Giveaway winner will be announced right back here! Remember we will never DM you from another account saying you’ve won. We’ll tag you on this post. Thanks for always being so supportive.

We will never forget September 11th, 2001 🇺🇸 our hearts ache today. We are teaching our children about those who died. Those who lived. Those who ran towards the chaos. Those who have suffered and continue to suffer. #alwaysremeber 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
📷 Thank you @justynealger for the beautiful photo that made my heart feel gratitude through today’s heartache ❤️
